--- 
name   : citron
version: 0.4.0
title  : Citron
summary: Classic Unit Testing
authors:
  - Thomas Sawyer <transfire@gmail.com>

description:
  Citron is a classical unit testing framework with
  a developer freindly DSL, runs on top of RubyTest
  and is BRASS compliant.

resources:
  home: http://rubyworks.github.com/citron
  code: http://github.com/rubyworks/citron
  bugs: http://github.com/rubyworks/citron/issues
  chat: irc://chat.us.freenode.net/rubyworks
  mail: http://groups.google.com/groups/rubyworks-mailinglist

repositories:
  upstream: git://github.com/proutils/citron.git

requirements:
  - rubytest
  - ae
  - detroit  (build)
  - reap     (build)
  - qed      (test)

organization: RubyWorks

